description:
Minor amendment to planning permission LBI ref: P070059 dated 03/07/2007 for the:
A]	adjustment to the height of both Blocks A and B and the floor level of Block B;
B]	re-modelling of access ramps to Block A and Block B and creation of new ramps to the approach and within the northern access around the Edwardian building; 
C]	provision of new windows and rearranged windows to Block A and B and removal of brise soleils to Block B; 
D]	internal alterations to student room sizes and layouts in Block A and B; and 
E]	omission of sub-station and creation of new lightwell to Block A.

decision_conditions:
INFORMATIVE: Amendments have been shown which respond to specific conditions imposed on the original planning permission.  As those details relate to conditions they cannot and have not been considered as part of this minor amendment application.  For clarity those amendments and their corresponding condition number are provided below:
-	Alterations to suggested materials (C3);
-	Removal of brise soleils to Block A (C4); 
-	Relocation of roof plant / lift overrun enclosures (C11); 
-	Provision of cycle parking (C18); and 
-	Alterations to landscaping (C24C25).
